  "comments": "<p>Strong UV activity on front:<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/604984d6b92f2.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/604984d6b92f2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br>© Max_505</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">On this 2018 note under UV at 365nm, the serial number on the right side fluoresces white:</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer ugc\" href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/67757900d913c.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/67757900d913c.jpg\"></a></p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">© Brandon Bertolli</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Blue iridescent stripe on reverse - inscription “HK 10” and flower:</p><p><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/67528b9504448.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/67528b9504448.jpg\"></a></p><p>© Kiet Tran</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The part of the pink squiggle over the transparent window is printed in colour-shifting ink - switches colours from pink to purple when the note is tilted. The denomination 10 is also inside the transparent window:</p><p><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/67528c63d0ac1.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/67528c63d0ac1.jpg\"></a><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/67528c6620549.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/67528c6620549.jpg\"></a></p><p>© Kiet Tran</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Latent image in the space to the right of the transparent window - denomination “10” can be seen when looked at closely or the note is tilted:</p><p><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/67528bf105103.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/67528bf105103.jpg\"></a></p><p>© Kiet Tran</p>",
